/* HTML5 display-role reset for older browsers */
article, aside, details, figcaption, figure,
footer, header, hgroup, main, menu, nav, section 
												display: block

/* HTML5 hidden-attribute fix for newer browsers */
*[hidden]
		display: none
body
	line-height: 1

ol, ul
	list-style: none

blockquote, q
			quotes: none

blockquote:before, blockquote:after,
q:before, q:after
				content: ''
				content: none

table 
	border-collapse: collapse
	border-spacing: 0
sources.sass\\_mixins.sass:
@mixin font($fontW,$fontS,$fontF: $font-base)
    font-family: $fontF
    font-weight: $fontW
    font-size: $fontS + px

@mixin backgound($url)
    background: url($url)
    background-repeat: no-repeat
    background-size: cover
    background-position: top center

@mixin link($color,$hover,$active)
    a
        color: $color
        &:hover
            color: $hover
        &:active
            color: $active

@mixin cover($color)
    content: ''
    display: block
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    left: 0
    width: 100%
    height: 100%
    background: $color

@mixin transform($anime,$opacity)
    transition: $anime
    opacity: $opacity

@mixin flex($direction)
    display: flex
    flex-direction: $direction
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center
    flex-wrap: wrap
sources.sass\\sections\\_header.sass:
@include link($color-text__primari,$color-primary,$color-secondary)

header
    background: $bg_gradient,url('../img/bg/bg-header.jpeg') no-repeat top center
    background-size: cover
    height: 1000px
    position: relative
    color: $color-text__primari
.header-menu
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    align-items: center
    padding: 40px 0 0 0
    // .logo
    //     text-transform: capitalize
    //     @include font(700,30)
    nav
        width: 625px
        .menu
            display: flex
            justify-content: space-around
            font-size: 14px
            &__item
            &__link
                text-transform: uppercase
                position: relative
                &:after
                    content: ''
                    display: block
                    position: absolute
                    width: 100%
                    height: 2px
                    bottom: -0px
                    background: #fce38a
                    transform: translateY(10px) scale(0)
                    transition: .3s ease
                &:hover
                    &:after
                        transform: translateY(10px) scale(1)
.header-content
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    align-items: center
    max-width: 805px
    text-align: center
    margin: 200px auto 200px
    &__title
        @include font(400,72,$font-title)
        margin: 0 0 40px 0
    &__heading
         @include font(bold,150)
         text-transform: uppercase

    &__line
        width: 60px
        height: 3px
        background: $color-text__primari
        margin: 70px 0 50px
    a.btn
        width: 160px
        height: 40px
        @include font(bold,14)
        line-height: 37px
        text-transform: uppercase
        border: 3px solid $color-text__primari
        text-align: center
        transition: all 1s
        &:hover
            border-color: $color-secondary
            transition: .5s ease
            color: $color-secondary
            transition: all 1s

sources.sass\\sections\\_wedo.sass:
.wedo
    width: 100%
    min-height: 900px
    &__content
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between
        margin: 90px 0 0 0
        &-image 
            width: 570px
.webo__akordion
            max-width: 600px
            width: 100%
            .card
                max-width: 600px
                width: 100%
                border: 1px solid $color-border
                margin: 0 0 10px
                &__top 
                    display: flex
                    justify-content: space-between
                    align-items: center
                    height: 60px
                    cursor: pointer
                    // border-bottom: 1px solid #cccc
                    padding: 0 15px
                &__title 
                    display: flex
                    align-items: center
                    text-transform: uppercase
                &__title img 
                    width: 30px
                    margin: 0 15px 0 0
                &__arrow
                    width: 22px
                &__arrow img:first-child 
                    display: none
                &__down 
                    padding: 15px
                    height: 180px
                    overflow-y: scroll
                    border-top: 1px solid $color-border 
                    display: none
                &__text
                    @include font(300,15,$font-text)
                    font-style: italic
                    color: $color-text__secondary
                    line-height: 1.5em
                    padding: 15px
sources.sass\\sections\\_slider-quote.sass:
.slider-quote
    width: 100%
    min-height: 290px
    background: #f8f8f8
.slider1
    width: 100%
    margin: 0 auto
    padding: 70px 0
    position: relative
    .pagonation
        &__right
            right: 0
        &__left
            left: 0
    .pagonation__right,
    .pagonation__left
        position: absolute
        font-size: 30px
        color: #cfcfcf
        top: 50%
        // margin-top: -15px
        transform: translateY(-50%)
    &__item
        @include flex(row)
        .square
            width: 150px
            height: 150px
            border: 3px solid $color-accent
            margin: 0 60px 0 0
            @include flex(row)
            &__icon  
                width: 63px 
        .slider-content
            max-width: 775px
            .section-content
                &__text
                    font-style: italic
                    font-size: 24px
                    margin: 0 0 25px
                    p::before,
                    p::after
                        content: '"'

                &__line
                    margin: 10px 10px 0 0
                &__title
                    text-transform: capitalize
            &__name
                display: flex
sources.sass\\sections\\_team.sass:
.team
    width: 100%
    min-height: 1050px
    &-members
        margin: 90px 0 0
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between
        flex-wrap: wrap
        .member
            @include flex(column)
            &__name
                line-height: 1.2
                margin: 27px 0 5px
            &__position
                @include font(300,15,$font-text)
                font-style: italic
                color: $color-text__secondary
                line-height: 1.6
        .photo-overlay__icons
            display: flex
            .icon-block
                width: 55px
                height: 55px
                background: $color-primary
                color: $color-secondary
                cursor: pointer
                border-right: 1px solid #f9bd87
                @include flex(column)
                font-size: 30px
                &:hover
                    background: $color-secondary
                    color: $color-text__primari
                    border-right: 0px
                    @include transform(.5s ease,1)
            & :last-child
                border-right: 0px

sources.sass\\sections\\_work.sass:
.work
    width: 100%
    min-height: 960px
    &-photo
        display: flex
        margin: 100px 0 0
.work-photo__left
            display: flex
            flex-wrap: wrap
            width: 50%
            .image1,.image2,.image3,.image4
                width: 50%
                position: relative
.work-photo__right
            display: flex
            width: 50%
            .image5,.image6,.image7
                width: 100%
                position: relative
            .wrapper-img
                width: 100% 
.image-overlay
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    left: 0
    right: 0
    bottom: 0
    background: $bg_gradient
    color: $color-text__primari
    display: none
    &__icon
        width: 30px
    &__title
        @include font(400,14)
        text-transform: uppercase
        margin: 20px 0
    &__text
        @include font(300,15,$font-text)
        font-style: italic

        


.image1:hover .image-overlay,
.image2:hover .image-overlay,
.image3:hover .image-overlay,
.image4:hover .image-overlay,
.image5:hover .image-overlay,
.image6:hover .image-overlay,
.image7:hover .image-overlay
    @include flex(column)

sources.sass\\sections\\_stories.sass:
.stories
    width: 100%
    min-height: 770px
    .blogs
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between
        flex-wrap: wrap
        .blog
            width: 380px
            &__photo
                width: 380px
                margin: 0 0 20px
                position: relative
            &__date
                width: 60px
                height: 70px
                position: absolute
                bottom: 10px
                left: -10px
                background: $color-accent
                @include flex(column)
                .content-date
                    @include flex(column)
                    color: $color-text__primari
                    &__number
                        @include font(700,30)
                    &__month
                        @include font(300,15,$font-text)
                        font-style: italic
                        text-transform: capitalize
            &__title
                margin: 0 0 15px
            &__text
                @include font(300,15,$font-text)
                line-height: 1.6
                color: $color-text__secondary
            &__line
                width: 100%
                height: 1px
                background: $color-border
                margin: 20px 0
            &__statistics
                display: flex
            &__views,
            &__comments
                @include font(300,15,$font-text)
                font-style: italic
                color: $color-text__secondary 
                display: flex 
                .view-icon
                    width: 20px
                    margin: 0 6px 0 0
                .comments-icon
                    width: 16px
                    margin: 0 6px 0 0
            &__views
                margin: 0 18px 0 0

sources.sass\\sections\\_footer.sass:
.footer
    width: 100%
    min-height: 500px
    &-content
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between
        flex-wrap: wrap
    &-contact
        max-width: 480px
        .logo
            font-size: 46px
            text-transform: capitalize
            margin: 70px 0 40px
            &__item
                color: $color-logo
                text-transform: capitalize
        &__text
            @include font(400,15,$font-text)
            color: $color-text__secondary
            line-height: 1.5em
            margin: 0 0 45px
        .folowers
            &__number
                @include font(700,18)
            &__text
        &__line
            width: 100%
            height: 1px
            background: $color-border
            margin: 19px 0 16px
.footer-icons
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    margin: 0 0 35px
    &__text
        @include font(400,15,$font-text)
        font-style: italic
        color: #b1b1b1
        margin: 0 25px 0 0
    &__img
        color: $color-accent
        font-size: 20px
        svg
            margin: 0 15px 0 0
.footer-contact__form
    display: flex
    height: 40px
    max-width: 380px
    input[type="text"]
        width: 230px
        border: 1px solid $color-border
        border-right: 0px
        &::placeholder
            padding: 0 13px
            @include font(400,15,$font-text)
            font-style: italic
            text-transform: capitalize
            color: $color-text__secondary
            outline: none
    input[type="button"]
        width: 150px
        border: 0px
        background: $color-accent
        @include font(700,14)
        text-transform: uppercase
        color: $color-text__primari
        cursor: pointer
        outline: none
        &:hover
            background: $color-accent_darcer
//footer-blogs
.footer-blogs
    max-width: 335px
    &__title
        margin: 95px 0 35px 0
.footer-blog
    display: flex
    margin: 0 0 20px 0
    &__img
        width: 120px
        margin: 0 20px 0 0
    &__about
    &__text
        text-transform: uppercase
        font-size: 12px
        line-height: 1.5em
        color: $color-text__title
    &__date
        @include font(300,13,$font-text)
        font-style: italic 
        color: $color-text__secondary
        line-height: 1.8em

// footer-insta
.footer-insta
    &__title
        margin: 95px 0 35px 0
    &__photos
        max-width: 270px
        display: flex
        flex-wrap: wrap
        img
            width: 88px
            margin: 0 2px 2px 0
